research_municipality_step.notes: The elected officials for Log Cabin city, TX, include the Mayor, Mayor Pro-Tem, and four Councilmembers. Information regarding a vacant council position for a 1-year unexpired term was noted in May 2025, but it is unclear if this position has since been filled. The roles of City Secretary, City Treasurer, City Attorney, and Volunteer Fire Chief are typically appointed positions and are not included as elected officials.
